main event: A UFO sighting involving a starlike object with trailing streaks of green, blue, and red was reported on May 9, 1961.
interesting points: The object was described as having a brightness comparable to a second magnitude star.,The sighting lasted for about 4-5 minutes.,The object was observed in a direction parallel to the Milky Way.,The report indicated that other crews would have been able to see the incident.,The altitude of the object was categorized as medium.
sighted object: starlike object with trailing streaks of color
